<li class="twitter share-on-twitter last"><a href="https://twitter.com/share?url=http%3A//www.pressprogress.ca/en/post/veterans-affairs-sees-confidence-management-plummet-new-low&amp;via=pressprogress&amp;text=Confidence%20in%20Veterans%20Affairs%20management%20plummets%20to%20new%20low%3A%20internal%20staff%20poll" title="Share Confidence in Veterans Affairs management plummets to new low: internal staff poll on Twitter" target="_blank"><i class="icon-twitter"></i>Share on Twitter</a></li>
